        "title_heading_type": "h4",
        "title_heading_size": "h4",
        "text": "<h2>Eat sleep live founded in 2004</h2><p>Eat Sleep Live was founded in 2004 by Mark Godsell-Fletcher. Driven by a lack of high quality wooden furniture to rival the mass produced alternatives, Mark saw the need for a more personal approach, working closely with our customers to create unique furniture solely made in the UK that will last a lifetime and beyond.<br/><br/>His first design was the Hudson dining table, hand-crafted from solid British reclaimed wood in a timeless design that is still going strong today. Seeing the incredible journey this beautiful wood had been on, a passion to give it a new lease of life was born.</p>",
        "button-text": "",
        "button-url": "",
